title: Vegetarian Food
typeOfFood: Vegan, Chinese, Thai, Fast food, Take-out
description: A relaxing place offering vegan vegetarian food, no alcohol. There is a noodle cart in front serving noodle soup and dry noodle. Inside is a buffet with around 8 different dishes each day (example: grilled "fish", massaman curry, red curry, stir fried vegetable). For 25B, you can get a bowl of noodle or a plate includes two vegetable dishes and rice. Extras available.
